Cartoon Filter Project

A real-time Cartoon Filter project built using Python and OpenCV.

Features:
- Real-time webcam processing
- Cartoon-style visual effect
- Beginner-friendly computer vision project

Technologies Used:
- Python
- OpenCV

How to Run:
1. Install Python
2. Install OpenCV:
   pip install opencv-python
3. Run the project:
   python cartoon.py

